item.description:
The first meeting at SunMoonStars Herbals went so well, we've decided to have "a regular monthly meeting" there on the third Saturday of every month!

Folks that live in other areas DON'T DESPAIR - we will schedule other meetings at other venues to make sure there is local participation for everyone! I'll be posting to the mailing list looking for other places/times the New England Metaphysical Club can meet... so please share your ideas on when/where you'd like other meetings to be.

The topic of this next meeting is still to be decided - if you can attend, please let us know what topic you're interested in. The general topic of "herbs" went very well and it seems like a group with a lot of fascinating interests! I'm sure we'll be able cover almost any topic.
item.how_to_find_us: The shop is only open for the New England Metaphysical Club at that hour.
item.name: February "Monthly Meeting In NH"
